                           書記官  吳佩蓁\r\n中    華    民    國    111   年     7    月     7    日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%e4%b8%8a%2c7%2c20220707%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDM,111,交簡上,7,20220707,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡上","JNO":"7","JDATE":"20220707","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}